### Notes
- Preserve original filters and `include/fields[]` across paginated requests.
- Avoid retries on 401/403; backoff with jitter on 429/503/504.

- ESLint v9+ requires flat config (`eslint.config.js`) with `@typescript-eslint/parser`; avoid legacy `.eslintrc.*` and `.eslintignore`.
- For n8n nodes, use `NodeConnectionType.Main` for `inputs`/`outputs` instead of string literals to satisfy type checks.

## Playbook Support Matrix (from `.docs/auvik/openapi-spec.json`)
- Alert triage: supported via `/alert/history/info` and `/alert/dismiss/{id}`
- Health snapshot: supported via `/inventory/device/info`, `/inventory/interface/info`, `/alert/history/info`, optional ASM via `/asm/client/info`
- Config drift: removed — Auvik API does not expose configuration content; attribute-only diffs provide limited value
- Maintenance windows: no public endpoint found → not supported
- Poller rollout: listing and devices via `/settings/snmppoller` and `/settings/snmppoller/{id}/devices`; no assignment endpoint → rollout write op not supported

